        <name xml:lang="en">dimethylacetamide</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Dimethylacetamide is a colorless liquid which is soluble in a wide variety of solvents. Dimethylacetamide is an excellent solvent and often acts as a catalyst in halogenation, cyclization, and alkylation reactions.
Dimethylacetamide is used in the spinning of polyacrylonitrile and as a solvent in the processing of other polymers.
Dimethylacetamide lithium chelate complexes intercalate cationic sites in layered silicates.</comment>
